---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Cookie Policy - AutiMind Inc."
  description="AutiMind Inc. cookie policy explaining how we use cookies to enhance your experience on our website."
  keywords="cookie policy, website cookies, AutiMind cookies, data tracking"
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="py-20 min-h-screen">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Cookie Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
          Last updated: January 1, 2025
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-300">
        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-teal-400 mb-4">About Cookies</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            This Cookie Policy explains how AutiMind, Inc. uses cookies and similar technologies on our website to enhance your browsing experience and improve our services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <section class="bg-gray-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-3">1. What Are Cookies</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
              <p>Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device when you visit our website. They help us understand how you interact with our site and enable certain functionalities.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="bg-gray-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-3">2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-teal-400 mb-2">Essential Cookies</h3>
                <p>Required for basic website functionality and security. These cannot be disabled.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-teal-400 mb-2">Analytics Cookies</h3>
                <p>Help us understand how visitors interact with our website to improve user experience.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-teal-400 mb-2">Functional Cookies</h3>
                <p>Enable enhanced functionality and personalization features.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="bg-gray-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-3">3. How We Use Cookies</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
              <p>We use cookies to:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
                <li>Ensure website security and proper functionality</li>
                <li>Analyze website traffic and usage patterns</li>
                <li>Improve website performance and user experience</li>
                <li>Remember your preferences and settings</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="bg-gray-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-3">4. Managing Cookies</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
              <p>You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences. However, disabling certain cookies may affect website functionality.</p>
              <p>Most browsers allow you to:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
                <li>View and delete cookies</li>
                <li>Block cookies from specific websites</li>
                <li>Block all cookies</li>
                <li>Delete cookies when you close your browser</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="bg-gray-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-3">5. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
              <p>We may use third-party services that place cookies on your device. These services have their own privacy policies and cookie practices.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="bg-gray-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-400 mb-3">6. Updates to This Policy</h2>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
              <p>We may update this Cookie Policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <div class="bg-teal-500/10 border border-teal-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-teal-400 mb-3">Questions About Cookies</h2>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
              <p>If you have questions about our use of cookies, contact us:</p>
              <p><strong>AutiMind, Inc.</strong></p>
              <p>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@autimind.com" class="text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300">privacy@autimind.com</a></p>
              <p>Address: Battle Creek, Michigan 49015</p>
              <p>Phone: 269.261.0069</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>